OL,5,MElectromagnetic Field is two weeks
OL,7,Maway!
OL,9,GHello! There’s only two weeks to go
OL,10,Gand somehow we still have plenty more
OL,11,Gto announce… Getting into the UK If
OL,12,Gyou are travelling from the EU you
OL,13,Gprobably don’t need to get a visa, but
OL,14,Gyou probably DO need to get an ETA:
OL,15,Ghttps://www.gov.uk/eta This is a new
OL,16,Grequirement since the last EMF - make
OL,17,Gsure you apply at least 3 working days
OL,18,Gbefore you set off. If you’re unsure
OL,19,Gwhether you require a visa please
OL,20,Gcheck. Family Workshops and NullSector
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
